---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
// Aca importaremos los componentes después
---
<Layout title="Tane Solution | Diseño Web para PYMES" description="Diseñamos páginas a medida, sin plantillas, y nos ocupamos de toda la parte técnica para que tú solo te enfoques en atender a tus nuevos clientes.">
  <main>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative pt-12 pb-16 lg:pt-20 lg:pb-24 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_top,var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-slate-800 via-slate-900 to-slate-900"></div>
      
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 text-center max-w-4xl">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 backdrop-blur-sm text-sm text-lime-400 font-medium mb-8">
          <span class="flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-lime-400"></span>
          Agencia nº1 en Diseño Web para Negocios Reales
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-8">
          Consigue la página web que tu negocio necesita: <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-linear-to-r from-lime-400 to-emerald-400">Rápida, Profesional y Diseñada para Atraer Clientes.</span>
        </h1>
        
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-400 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Tu negocio local no debería ser un secreto. Olvídate de plantillas baratas y procesos técnicos interminables. Diseñamos tu web a medida en tiempo récord.
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="#precios" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 bg-lime-400 hover:bg-lime-500 text-slate-900 font-bold rounded-xl transition-all hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 shadow-[0_0_40px_-10px_rgba(163,230,53,0.3)]">
            👉 Quiero mi web profesional
          </a>
          <a href="#demos" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 border border-slate-700 text-white font-semibold rounded-xl transition-all">
            Ver ejemplos
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-12 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-400">
          <div class="flex -space-x-2">
            <!-- Simulated avatars -->
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-700 border-2 border-slate-900 flex items-center justify-center text-xs">J</div>
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-600 border-2 border-slate-900 flex items-center justify-center text-xs">M</div>
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-500 border-2 border-slate-900 flex items-center justify-center text-xs">S</div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-1 text-yellow-400 ml-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"></path></svg>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"></path></svg>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"></path></svg>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"></path></svg>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <span>Proceso rápido y sin dolores de cabeza.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Agitación del Problema -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-slate-900 border-t border-slate-800">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-16">¿Te suena familiar alguna de estas historias?</h2>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-700/50 p-8 rounded-2xl">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-500/10 text-red-400 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white">"Mi web actual es de 2010"</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Tus clientes te buscan en Google, ven una web lenta, desactualizada o directamente fea, y se van a la competencia que transmite más confianza.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-700/50 p-8 rounded-2xl">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-500/10 text-orange-400 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z"></path><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white">"Intenté hacerla yo mismo..."</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Pasaste horas peleándote con tutoriales de YouTube o Wix para darte cuenta de que no tienes tiempo para eso y el resultado no transmite tu calidad.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-700/50 p-8 rounded-2xl">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-yellow-500/10 text-yellow-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white">"Agencias que tardan meses"</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Has pedido presupuestos y te hablan con tecnicismos, te piden precios desorbitados y te dan plazos de entrega que parecen un chiste.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <p class="text-center text-xl text-slate-300 mt-16 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Tu página web no debería ser un dolor de cabeza ni un pozo de gastos inútil. Debería ser <span class="text-lime-400 font-bold">tu mejor trabajador: disponible 24/7 para convencer a tus clientes.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
<!-- Beneficios -->
    <section id="beneficios" class="py-24 bg-slate-800">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-16 items-center">
          <div class="lg:w-1/2" data-reveal="left">
            <div class="relative w-full aspect-square md:aspect-video lg:aspect-square bg-slate-800/40 rounded-3xl border border-slate-700/50 overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center p-8">
              <!-- Grid Background -->
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,#ffffff05_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,#ffffff05_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-size-[32px_32px]"></div>
              
              <!-- Floating UI Elements -->
              <div class="relative w-full max-w-sm">
                <!-- Main Window -->
                <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl border border-slate-700 shadow-2xl overflow-hidden relative z-10 animate-[float_6s_ease-in-out_infinite]">
                  <div class="h-8 bg-slate-800/80 border-b border-slate-700 flex items-center px-4 gap-2">
                    <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-400"></div>
                    <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-400"></div>
                    <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-emerald-400"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="p-6">
                    <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-xl bg-lime-400/20 text-lime-400 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                      <svg class="w-10 h-10" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="w-full h-4 bg-slate-800 rounded mb-3"></div>
                    <div class="w-3/4 h-4 bg-slate-800 rounded"></div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Floating Stats Card (Behind left) -->
                <div class="absolute -left-8 -bottom-8 w-48 bg-slate-800/90 backdrop-blur-md border border-slate-700 rounded-2xl p-4 shadow-xl z-20 animate-[float_5s_ease-in-out_infinite_2s]">
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                    <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-emerald-400/20 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400">
                      <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Ventas</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="w-full h-2 bg-slate-700 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="w-4/5 h-full bg-lime-400"></div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Floating Code block (Right) -->
                <div class="absolute -right-6 top-12 w-48 bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-4 shadow-xl z-0 animate-[float_7s_ease-in-out_infinite_1s]">
                  <div class="w-full h-2 bg-slate-800 rounded mb-2"></div>
                  <div class="w-5/6 h-2 bg-slate-800 rounded mb-2"></div>
                  <div class="w-4/6 h-2 bg-slate-800 rounded"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="lg:w-1/2">
            <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold mb-10">Diseño a medida, resultados reales y cero dolores de cabeza técnicos.</h2>
            <div class="space-y-8">
              <div class="flex gap-4">
                <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-lime-400/10 text-lime-400 flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Construcción Ultra Rápida</h3>
                  <p class="text-slate-400">Lanzamos tu web en tiempo récord. Sin esperas interminables que estancan tu lanzamiento.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="flex gap-4">
                <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-lime-400/10 text-lime-400 flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zm0 0h12a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2.343M11 7.343l1.657-1.657a2 2 0 012.828 0l2.829 2.829a2 2 0 010 2.828l-8.486 8.485M7 17h.01"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">100% Personalizado</h3>
                  <p class="text-slate-400">Nada de plantillas genéricas. Tu negocio es único y diseñamos tu marca para que destaque por encima de tu competencia local.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex gap-4">
                <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-lime-400/10 text-lime-400 flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z"></path><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Gestión Llave en Mano</h3>
                  <p class="text-slate-400">Dominamos toda la tecnología. Hosting, SEO base, velocidad... nosotros lo dejamos resuelto. Tú solo apruebas el resultado y cobras a tus clientes.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Demos / Portfolio -->
    <section id="demos" class="py-24 bg-slate-900">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Echa un vistazo a lo que podemos crear para ti</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">No importa tu sector, adaptamos la estrategia y el diseño a lo que tus clientes reales están buscando.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Demo 1 -->
          <div class="group cursor-pointer">
            <div class="relative w-full aspect-4/3 bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden mb-4 border border-slate-700 shadow-lg">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-slate-700 m-2 rounded-xl flex flex-col overflow-hidden transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-105">
                <div class="h-4 bg-slate-800 w-full flex items-center px-2">
                   <div class="flex gap-1"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-600"></div><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-600"></div></div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-4 bg-linear-to-b from-blue-900/50 to-slate-800 flex-1">
                   <div class="w-1/2 h-4 bg-blue-400/20 rounded mb-2"></div>
                   <div class="w-3/4 h-6 bg-white/10 rounded mb-6"></div>
                   <div class="w-20 h-6 bg-blue-500/80 rounded-full"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">Clínica Dental / Salud</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Diseño enfocado en confianza y reservas de citas rápidas.</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Demo 2 -->
          <div class="group cursor-pointer">
            <div class="relative w-full aspect-4/3 bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden mb-4 border border-slate-700 shadow-lg">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-slate-700 m-2 rounded-xl flex flex-col overflow-hidden transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-105">
                <div class="h-4 bg-slate-800 w-full flex items-center px-2">
                   <div class="flex gap-1"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-600"></div><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-600"></div></div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-4 bg-linear-to-b from-stone-800 to-slate-800 flex-1 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
                   <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-stone-600/50 mb-3"></div>
                   <div class="w-3/4 h-5 bg-white/10 rounded mb-2"></div>
                   <div class="w-1/2 h-3 bg-white/5 rounded"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">Abogados y Gestoría</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Estructura seria, profesional con captación de Leads.</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Demo 3 -->
          <div class="group cursor-pointer">
            <div class="relative w-full aspect-4/3 bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden mb-4 border border-slate-700 shadow-lg">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-slate-700 m-2 rounded-xl flex flex-col overflow-hidden transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-105">
                <div class="h-4 bg-slate-800 w-full flex items-center px-2">
                   <div class="flex gap-1"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-600"></div><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-600"></div></div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-4 bg-linear-to-br from-amber-900/40 to-slate-800 flex-1 flex gap-2">
                   <div class="w-1/2 bg-amber-500/10 rounded-lg"></div>
                   <div class="w-1/2 flex flex-col gap-2">
                     <div class="h-10 bg-white/10 rounded-lg"></div>
                     <div class="flex-1 bg-white/5 rounded-lg"></div>
                   </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">Reformas Externas</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Visuales potentes de antes y después con presupuesto ágil.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-12 text-center">
          <a href="#precios" class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 text-white font-semibold rounded-xl transition-all">Quiero un resultado así para mi negocio</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Proceso -->
    <section id="proceso" class="py-24 bg-slate-800 border-t border-slate-700/50">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-16">De la idea a tener tu web vendiendo en solo 3 pasos</h2>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 relative">
          <!-- Connector line -->
          <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-[45px] left-[10%] right-[10%] h-0.5 bg-slate-700 z-0"></div>
          
          <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
            <div class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-slate-900 border-4 border-slate-700 flex items-center justify-center text-3xl font-black text-slate-500 mb-6 shadow-xl">1</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Reserva tu llamada</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400">Hablamos 15 mins por videollamada o WhatsApp para entender tu negocio y qué necesitas. Cero agobios ni compromisos.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
            <div class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-slate-900 border-4 border-lime-400 shadow-[0_0_30px_-5px_rgba(163,230,53,0.4)] flex items-center justify-center text-3xl font-black text-lime-400 mb-6">2</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Diseño y Propuesta</h3>
